welcome_message_body: "Welcome to Dukinfield, a charming town in the heart of the United Kingdom. Known for its friendly community and picturesque landscapes, we invite you to immerse yourself in its beauty and discover all it has to offer. Enjoy your stay!"

terminals.name: Terminal 1
terminals.description: The main terminal for international flights at Manchester Airport.

terminals.name: Terminal 2
terminals.description: The secondary terminal for domestic and some international flights at Manchester Airport.

terminals.name: Terminal 3
terminals.description: The newest terminal at Manchester Airport, primarily used for low-cost airlines.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport, but a premium option is also available for faster speeds.
